@plan "PPL Hypertrophy"
@freq 6x/week
@cycle 4w: w1-3 progress, w4 deload
@unit kg

# ============================================================
# PUSH — Brust, Schultern, Trizeps
# ============================================================

---[Push] Mo Do

Bench Press          4x8   @RPE8  r120s  +2.5kg/w
OHP                  3x10  @RPE7  r90s
ss {
  Incline DB Fly     3x12  r60s
  Tricep Pushdown    3x15  r60s
}
Lateral Raise        4x15  r60s  drop
Face Pull            3x15  r60s

> Aufwärmen: 2x10 @50%, 1x5 @70% vor Bench Press

# ============================================================
# PULL — Rücken, Bizeps
# ============================================================

---[Pull] Di Fr

Deadlift             3x5   @RPE9  r180s  +2.5kg/w
Barbell Row          4x8   @RPE8  r120s
ss {
  Lat Pulldown       3x10
  Face Pull          3x15
}
ss {
  Hammer Curl        3x12
  Rear Delt Fly      3x15
}

> Woche 4 (Deload): Deadlift nur 3x5 @60%

# ============================================================
# LEGS — Beine, Gesäß
# ============================================================

---[Legs] Mi Sa

Squat                4x6   @RPE8  r180s  +2.5kg/w  t3010
RDL                  3x10  @RPE7  r120s
ss {
  Leg Press          3x12
  Leg Curl           3x12
}
Bulgarian Split Squat 3x10 @RPE7  r90s
Calf Raise           4x15  r60s

> Bei Knieproblemen: Beinpresse statt Squat
